		- bedrift *
		- papp2 *
		- sport		(times out)

	* Revoked


	Problematic subdomains:

		- atorget *
		- bedriftfiles		(self-signed, mismatched, CN: hotelladmin.aftenposten.no)
		- bil *
		- godetilbud *
		- kundeservice		(revoked)
